    "# 🏥 MediCare Hospital Assistant — Capstone Project\n",
    "**Agentic AI Course 2026 | Dr. Kanthi Kiran Sirra**\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "**Domain:** Healthcare / Hospital Information  \n",
    "**User:** Patients and visitors of MediCare General Hospital, Hyderabad  \n",
    "**Problem:** The hospital helpline receives 200+ calls/day, 80% asking the same 5 questions. Staff are overwhelmed. We need a 24/7 intelligent patient assistant that knows the hospital, remembers the conversation, and never fabricates information.  \n",
    "**Success:** Agent correctly answers OPD, fees, appointments, insurance, emergency queries from KB; admits uncertainty for unknown topics; maintains context across turns.  \n",
    "**Tool:** DateTime tool — patients often ask 'Is the OPD open now?' requiring current date/time.\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
