    "        'question': 'What insurance providers does MediCare accept?',\n",
    "        'ground_truth': 'MediCare accepts Star Health, United India, New India Assurance, HDFC ERGO, ICICI Lombard, Bajaj Allianz, Religare, and Aditya Birla Health Insurance among others.'\n",
    "    },\n",
    "    {\n",
